					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialog when interactin with the shrine dedicated to Helm in Stormshore Tabernacle. All players will be able to read some lore about the god. Additionally, if the player is a cleric of Helm, they'll be able to give offerings and pray/communicate with the god to get a blessing."
